For every n from 1 to 15, do the following:
    If n is divisible by 15, say "FizzBuzz".
    Otherwise, if n is divisible by 3, say "Fizz".
    Otherwise, if n is divisible by 5, say "Buzz".
    Otherwise, say n.

# Expected output:
# 1
# 2
# Fizz
# 4
# Buzz
# Fizz
# 7
# 8
# Fizz
# Buzz
# 11
# Fizz
# 13
# 14
# FizzBuzz
